version_description: My version has more nuanced chording and tabs for specific parts, including the intricate intro.
Complete and well-aligned chords / two versions (with and without capo) / suggestions for playable voicings.
Chords placed at the exact spot (I think) and with chords per measure
Easier to follow and more accurate.
Chords for all vocal and instrumental parts / slash chords featuring the descending bass line / suggestions for playable voicings and tab for turnaround / audio link to a demo recording of the tab.
Contains a simplified chord layout with the chords over the correct lyrics in the correct location.
Has the subtle passing chords, particularly in the choruses, and the bass notes. Chord legend included.
More in depth chords are used, giving more experienced players the option to make the song sound more like the original, with the original having been played on the piano.
